<span id="Description"></span>
==Beschreibung==

Der Befehl '''Part Auswahlfilter''' wird benutzt, um die Auswahl in der [[3D_view/de|3D-Ansicht]] auf Scheitelpunkte, Kanten oder Flächen einzuschränken, oder diese Einschränkung zu entfernen.

<span id="Usage"></span>
==Anwendung==

<span id="24px_Vertex_selection"></span>
===[[Image:Vertex-selection.svg|24px]] Knotenauswahl===

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
# This option only allows the selection of vertices.
# There are several ways to invoke this option:
#* Click on the black down arrow to the right of the {{Button|[[Image:Part_SelectFilter.svg|16px]]}} button in the toolbar and select the {{MenuCommand|[[Image:Vertex-selection.svg|16px]] Vertex selection}} option from the flyout. Note: the button image will change depending on the selected option.
#* Use the keyboard shortcut: {{KEY|X}} then {{KEY|S}}.
</div>

<span id="24px_Edge_selection"></span>
===[[Image:Edge-selection.svg|24px]] Kantenauswahl===

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
# This option only allows the selection of edges.
# There are several ways to invoke this option:
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|[[Image:Edge-selection.svg|16px]] Edge selection}} option from the toolbar. See above.
#* Use the keyboard shortcut: {{KEY|E}} then {{KEY|S}}.
</div>

<span id="24px_Face_selection"></span>
===[[Image:Face-selection.svg|24px]] Flächenauswahl===

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
# This option only allows the selection of faces.
# There are several ways to invoke this option:
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|[[Image:Face-selection.svg|16px]] Face selection}} option from the toolbar. See above.
#* Use the keyboard shortcut: {{KEY|F}} then {{KEY|S}}.
</div>

<span id="24px_All_selection_filters_cleared"></span>
===[[Image:Clear-selection.svg|24px]] Alle Auswahlfilter löschen===

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
# This option allows the selection of all subelements and of whole objects.
# There are several ways to invoke this option:
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|[[Image:Clear-selection.svg|16px]] All selection filters cleared}} option from the toolbar. See above.
#* Use the keyboard shortcut: {{KEY|C}} then {{KEY|S}}.
</div>

<span id="Notes"></span>
==Hinweise==

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* Selecting from the [[Tree_view|Tree view]] is impossible with the vertex, edge and face selection options.
* The vertex, edge and face selection options do not work together with [[Std_BoxSelection|Std BoxSelection]] or [[Std_BoxElementSelection|Std BoxElementSelection]].
</div>


